    <item>
      <title>预计感恩节期间美国各地将出现冬季风暴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-24/forecasts-warn-of-possible-winter-storms-across-us-during-thanksgiving-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加利福尼亚州温莎（美联社）——美国各地的气象预报员发出警告，又一轮冬季天气可能给感恩节假期前的旅行带来困难，而加利福尼亚州和华盛顿州仍在继续从风暴破坏和停电中恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-11-24/forecasts-warn-of-possible-winter-storms-across-us-during-thanksgiving-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 08:16:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及国内电力需求下降，重新评估液化天然气进口需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/egypt-reviewing-lng-import-needs-as-domestic-power-demand-dips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及最近转移了一批进口液化天然气，在国内电力需求下降和削减开支的背景下，该国正在重新评估其能源进口需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/egypt-reviewing-lng-import-needs-as-domestic-power-demand-dips</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 08:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员警告称，英国基金因国内投资不足面临税收风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/uk-funds-risk-tax-hit-for-underinvesting-at-home-official-warns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国商业银行行长在警告称，在政府推行一项关键增长计划之际，英国可能会收回未能在国内进行足够投资的资产管理公司的养老金税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/uk-funds-risk-tax-hit-for-underinvesting-at-home-official-warns</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿达尼被美国证券交易委员会传唤解释贿赂案立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-summoned-by-us-sec-to-explain-position-in-bribery-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据印度报业托拉斯报道，印度亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼和他的侄子萨加尔阿达尼被美国证券交易委员会传唤，解释他们为赢得太阳能合同而支付了超过 2.5 亿美元的贿赂的指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-24/adani-summoned-by-us-sec-to-explain-position-in-bribery-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2024 04:41:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
