      <title>美国通胀持续高企将强化美联储的缓慢政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/stubborn-us-inflation-set-to-reinforce-the-fed-s-go-slow-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来一周美国通胀数据显示价格压力依然顽固，这将强化美联储对未来降息的谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-23/stubborn-us-inflation-set-to-reinforce-the-fed-s-go-slow-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
